assemblage.p:
The equation of a hyperbola with center at the origin is
        \blert{\frac{x^2}{a^2} - \frac{y^2}{b^2} = 1} \qquad
                \text{ or } \qquad \blert{\frac{y^2}{b^2} -\frac{x^2}{a^2}  = 1}

